"It mined itself. Its self-mining depleted uranium" said the pig.

"With a shovel" said the pig.
And the wolf was like, "that's pretty cool and all but I really meant how did you mine it from the ground?"


"It mined itself. Its self-mining depleted uranium" said the pig.
And the wolf was like, "that is so cool!"

And the wolf was like, "can I come in and see it?"


nd the pig was like, "sure" and he let the wolf in.


The wolf advanced toward the pig. "I'd stop if I were you," said the pig, and reached for a nearby wand. Holding the wand near his belly a loud clicking filled the room.

Whats that?" asked the wolf.
 "A Geiger counter" said the pig. "If you eat me you will get radiation sickness and die."
"Oh" said the wolf, "that sucks, I was really looking forward to eating you."


"I know you were", said the pig, and hit the wolf over the head with the Geiger counter. The wolf collapsed.
And the pig was like, "good riddance".
 He then stuffed the wolf into the over and set it on "bake."
When the wolf was fully cooked the pig ate him.
